import React from "react"; import formatDate from '../util/formatDate.js'; class Avg extends React.Component { render () { const {houses} = this.props; return(
no country city address latitude longtitude parcel_m2 gross_m2 net_m2 rooms price link market date images
{index+1} {itemJson.country} {itemJson.city} {itemJson.address} {itemJson.lat} {itemJson.lng} {itemJson.parcel_m2} {itemJson.gross_m2} {itemJson.net_m2} {itemJson.rooms} {itemJson.value.toString() + " " + itemJson.currency} {itemJson.link} {formatDate(itemJson.market_date)} {itemJson.img_link.length}
) } } export default Avg;
